=============
IWKmail 0.0.2
=============

  - Misc memory management fixes.
  - Properly load POP3 accounts if disconnected.

=============
IWKmail 0.0.1
=============

First release. Very basic mail experience.

  - Implemented basic browsing of accounts, folders and messages.
  - Protocols supported: IMAP, POP, SMTP.
  - Allow to create and delete accounts.
  - Some preconfigured settings available.
  - Messages management: delete, mark as (un)read.
  - Message details view.
  - Uses GNOME keyring for storing passwords.
  - Outbox and message send in plain text.
  - (Un)block external images in messages.
  - Save to drafts folder (still not implemented opening them
    again).
